## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="26d30-102">一旦创建了一个线程，该线程将处于至少一种 <xref:System.Threading.ThreadState> 状态直到终止。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="26d30-102">Once a thread is created, it is in at least one of the <xref:System.Threading.ThreadState> states until it terminates.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="26d30-103">`ThreadStateException` 由于线程的当前状态而无法执行所请求操作的方法引发。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="26d30-103">`ThreadStateException` is thrown by methods that cannot perform the requested operation due to the current state of a thread.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="26d30-104">例如，尝试通过在已终止的线程上调用来重新启动中止 <xref:System.Threading.Thread.Start%2A> 的线程会引发 <xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="26d30-104">For example, trying to restart an aborted thread by calling <xref:System.Threading.Thread.Start%2A> on a thread that has terminated throws a <xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="26d30-105"><xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException> 使用 HRESULT COR_E_THREADSTATE，其值为0x80131520。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="26d30-105"><xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException> uses the HRESULT COR_E_THREADSTATE, which has the value 0x80131520.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="26d30-106">有关实例的初始属性值的列表<xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException>，请参阅<xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException.%23ctor%2A>构造函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="26d30-106">For a list of initial property values for an instance of <xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException>, see the <xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException.%23ctor%2A> constructors.</span></span>  
  
   
  
